{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T15:59:38.219Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Computer Use Safety"},{"type":"text","text":" encompasses Anthropic's comprehensive security framework for protecting users when Claude controls computers through visual interaction—a capability that grants AI full system access and introduces unique risks like malware creation, cyber attacks, and scaled abuse."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Computer Use Safety is a set of "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"technical safeguards, policy restrictions, and implementation requirements"},{"type":"text","text":" designed to prevent malicious use of Anthropic's Computer Use feature, which enables AI agents to:\n- Click anywhere on screen\n- Type keyboard input\n- Navigate any software\n- Access files and systems"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Unlike traditional API calls, Computer Use gives Claude "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"direct control over a computer"},{"type":"text","text":", making safety critical."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"New risks introduced by Computer Use"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Risk"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"parag